      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", is now resumed. The persons meant are the three chiefs of the Levitical guilds of musicians, Heman, Asaph, and Ethan; their “children” are the members of those guilds. (Comp. the phrase, “sons of the prophets,” ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
